<lb n="3" break="no"/>ḻanallūril Ūṟṟukkāṭuṭaiyāṉ vaṭukaṉ pava<unclear>ḻa</unclear>kkuṉṟāna rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>taṉañciya muven=ta veḷāṉ cantiviḷakku Oṉṟukku viṭṭa
